{"tid":554343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一年同男友過情人節","createTime":"2018-02-08T11:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T14:20:51.000Z","uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"74060b9ac77db516b609abba7e9f90e1bc3643f5","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"我哋都唔係啲好著重物質嘅人<br />\n一齊咗差唔多一年 <br />\n就算係紀念日/大時大節都唔會送啲咩俾對方<br />\n連聖誕節都冇互送禮物 亦冇食咩大餐 <br />\n只係周圍行下湊下熱鬧咁已經覺得好滿足<br />\n情人節我硬係覺得要做啲嘢<br />\n例如寫心意卡 整朱古力嗰類<br />\n<br />\n送又好似同我哋原本嘅相處模式好唔同<br />\n唔送又好似好懶 唔付出咁<br />\n究竟我應該點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c251268c911f39db3e592eaf3d902a595c827226","tid":554343,"uid":36435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"錫一啖當禮物"},{"pid":"5672ca85368e245fd51cb241e2f901cd0c05fad1","tid":554343,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"俾佢口爆/中出/屌屎眼"},{"pid":"d87fd5263a2d91ec06f56b4df3ef942cecb5583a","tid":554343,"uid":47480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"佢唔食朱古力 點算"},{"pid":"eb7251038269c49aac5a636bdbaac0abe8a7938d","tid":554343,"uid":138981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"繼續唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87defa6eed59fb0f7110ea256f1d563ff7421f7","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錫一啖當禮物</blockquote><br />\n咁佢都收過好多份禮物喇喎 <br />\n認真問 有冇咩好提議"},{"pid":"2fb4fc633962adf3f7798979cdf4c56700443003","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔食朱古力 點算</blockquote><br />\n就係知佢食先整架嘛"},{"pid":"cc41a1056f1f0209a2a198d0bdce65a124abe55e","tid":554343,"uid":56240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"比隻豬佢"},{"pid":"830c1d63e417e0f84d08292747490defa9ca3bb0","tid":554343,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b87defa6eed59fb0f7110ea256f1d563ff7421f7","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錫一啖當禮物</blockquote><br />\n咁佢都收過好多份禮物喇喎 <br />\n認真問 有冇咩好提議"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:35:42.000Z","msg":"整下皮革野囉 佢鍾唔鍾意皮㗎"},{"pid":"d7ed3a4d1ed54962836ea646b81e71ce8b893daa","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錫一啖當禮物</blockquote><br />\n咁佢都收過好多份禮物喇喎 <br />\n認真問 有冇咩好提議</blockquote>整下皮革野囉 佢鍾唔鍾意皮㗎</blockquote><br />\n依家整仲整得切咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d6ec7e7a5ea57074972eb5e4290dddde820eb0","tid":554343,"uid":13583,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"寫封信講你嘅對佢嘅感受  加handmade 朱古力<br />\n信重要過禮物<br />\n咁先反映到你係唔想改變原本嘅相處模式 ，反而係想藉住依個節日勇敢啲向佢表達心中所想<br />\n記住，節日存在嘅意義係透過傳統活動去加深/增進人與人之間嘅感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聖誕節同家人交換禮物係想關心下家人嘅喜好/有咩需要，感恩節食火雞食想多謝果啲幫過自己嘅人，清明節掃墓係思念/記念故人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後祝福絲打同男朋友<br />\n亦都承勸各位諗清楚你係要想段關係定係份禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19636bb29dd984dfaeb3b524b96b64ba6f14cdae","tid":554343,"uid":125770,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"斬你隻手出嚟煎俾佢食"},{"pid":"a751b568529cadea70863f2df8824364e3c10864","tid":554343,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7ed3a4d1ed54962836ea646b81e71ce8b893daa","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>錫一啖當禮物</blockquote><br />\n咁佢都收過好多份禮物喇喎 <br />\n認真問 有冇咩好提議</blockquote>整下皮革野囉 佢鍾唔鍾意皮㗎</blockquote><br />\n依家整仲整得切咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"未整過唔知要整幾耐喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁啪啪啪算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885fd01ebb22beafa3ff3d8f05e53708d620e373","tid":554343,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fb4fc633962adf3f7798979cdf4c56700443003","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔食朱古力 點算</blockquote><br />\n就係知佢食先整架嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bb39740548017ac6ec6789a8e3a8a54a802ead","tid":554343,"uid":54451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"認真答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扑嘢就夠"},{"pid":"d0f45b023c390f9af0d9874a218db1f3bf5a313b","tid":554343,"uid":168685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"我都係第一年過情人節 唔知送咩好<br />\n最後決定禮物+朱古力 pack埋一個盒俾佢<br />\n1516緊寫唔寫卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7808086be500854fc5d2bb8f622a9394206e14d5","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫封信講你嘅對佢嘅感受  加handmade 朱古力<br />\n信重要過禮物<br />\n咁先反映到你係唔想改變原本嘅相處模式 ，反而係想藉住依個節日勇敢啲向佢表達心中所想<br />\n記住，節日存在嘅意義係透過傳統活動去加深/增進人與人之間嘅感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聖誕節同家人交換禮物係想關心下家人嘅喜好/有咩需要，感恩節食火雞食想多謝果啲幫過自己嘅人，清明節掃墓係思念/記念故人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後祝福絲打同男朋友<br />\n亦都承勸各位諗清楚你係要想段關係定係份禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完好似更加清楚自己想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd094462b91518e7317a41b0e4f9a576a19b7a7","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係第一年過情人節 唔知送咩好<br />\n最後決定禮物+朱古力 pack埋一個盒俾佢<br />\n1516緊寫唔寫卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我之前都諗咗好耐寫唔寫<br />\n因為我係嗰啲唔太鍾意表達自己心意嘅人<br />\n不過前幾日諗完 都覺得寫下卡幾好<br />\nbtw好奇問下 絲打買左咩禮物呀"},{"pid":"fe6f6d466e72573f09a0a188067fcf47e168f0f6","tid":554343,"uid":13583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7808086be500854fc5d2bb8f622a9394206e14d5","tid":554343,"uid":162884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫封信講你嘅對佢嘅感受  加handmade 朱古力<br />\n信重要過禮物<br />\n咁先反映到你係唔想改變原本嘅相處模式 ，反而係想藉住依個節日勇敢啲向佢表達心中所想<br />\n記住，節日存在嘅意義係透過傳統活動去加深/增進人與人之間嘅感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聖誕節同家人交換禮物係想關心下家人嘅喜好/有咩需要，感恩節食火雞食想多謝果啲幫過自己嘅人，清明節掃墓係思念/記念故人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後祝福絲打同男朋友<br />\n亦都承勸各位諗清楚你係要想段關係定係份禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完好似更加清楚自己想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"唔駛客氣  :<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf03907dd438436b0c1c060908ff8a3789a68a2","tid":554343,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0f45b023c390f9af0d9874a218db1f3bf5a313b","tid":554343,"uid":168685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"我都係第一年過情人節 唔知送咩好<br />\n最後決定禮物+朱古力 pack埋一個盒俾佢<br />\n1516緊寫唔寫卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T13:42:03.000Z","msg"